{"type":"message","id":"80f0cebd","parentId":"90ff1908","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:10:56.169Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sr04uykzy4o7_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[32;1mName                      [0m[32;1m LastWriteTime[0m\r\n[32;1m----                      [0m [32;1m-------------[0m\r\npulse_2026-03-24 081017.md 3/24/2026 8:10:49 AM\r\npulse_2026-03-24 080821.md 3/24/2026 8:08:42 AM\r\npulse_2026-03-24 080517.md 3/24/2026 8:05:25 AM"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1081,"aggregated":"[32;1mName                      [0m[32;1m LastWriteTime[0m\r\n[32;1m----                      [0m [32;1m-------------[0m\r\npulse_2026-03-24 081017.md 3/24/2026 8:10:49 AM\r\npulse_2026-03-24 080821.md 3/24/2026 8:08:42 AM\r\npulse_2026-03-24 080517.md 3/24/2026 8:05:25 AM","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774354256167}}
{"type":"message","id":"906c15f1","parentId":"80f0cebd","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:10:59.092Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"A new pulse log was created at 08:10:17. Let me read it.","thinkingSignature":"f211a54dc6b025ac6d13d982741bc798bc4640d2971787a049852b929031f721"},{"type":"text","text":"A new pulse just completed. Let me read it.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h7sy718sm2gs_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\pulse_2026-03-24 081017.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1651,"output":83,"cacheRead":12137,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13871,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774354256170}}
{"type":"message","id":"7c1179ea","parentId":"906c15f1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:10:59.099Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_h7sy718sm2gs_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 081017\n\n## Applied Mutations\nJust applied: research/TIC-EXPERIMENT.md (appended)\n\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and determine what single concrete action to take.\r\n\r\nCurrent situation:\r\n- Phase 0 and Phase 1 COMPLETE\r\n- Gap-Decay synthesis done\r\n- LLM-Augmented pulse working\r\n- TIC Experiment is the next pending action\r\n- A TIC-EXPERIMENT.md doc was just appended\r\n\r\nThe pending TIC Experiment requires:\r\n1. Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n2. Measure invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n3. Predict next pulse content from invariants\r\n4. Validate against success criteria (>70%, >60%)\r\n\r\nLooking at what's immediately actionable - I should start implementing the TIC classifier. Let me look at what files exist and what I can do.\r\n\r\nThe TIC experiment needs:\r\n- Access to pulse logs in `logs/` directory\r\n- A classifier to determine invariant vs variant content\r\n- Prediction capability for next pulse\r\n\r\nA concrete action could be:\r\n1. Write a script to analyze pulse logs and extract invariants/variants\r\n2. Create the TIC classifier implementation\r\n3. Start processing the pulse logs\r\n\r\nLet me check what pulse log files exist and start building the TIC classifier. The most concrete immediate action would be to implement the classifier script.\r\n\r\nI'll create a TIC classifier script that:\r\n- Reads pulse logs\r\n- Identifies invariant structure (goals, pending items, notes that persist)\r\n- Identifies variant content (new observations, actions, reflections)\r\n- Tests prediction capability\r\n\r\nLet me write a PowerShell script for this since we're in a Windows environment and pulse.ps1 is PowerShell.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC experiment is the critical next step, but I need to implement the classifier before running it. The pulse logs in `logs/` contain the raw material - I should create the TIC classifier script that will analyze them for invariant/variant patterns and test prediction accuracy.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate `scripts/tic-classifier.ps1` - the PowerShell implementation of the Temporal Invariance Compression classifier that will process pulse logs, classify invariant vs variant content, and measure prediction accuracy against the success criteria.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # TIC Classifier - Temporal Invariance Compression\r\n# Analyzes pulse logs for invariant/variant classification\r\n# Tests next-pulse prediction from invariant structure\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$MinPulseCount = 5,\r\n    [double]$PredictionThreshold = 0.6,\r\n    [string]$LogPattern = \"logs/pulse_*.md\"\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Continue\"\r\n\r\n# ============================================\r\n# INVARIANT DETECTION\r\n# ============================================\r\nfunction Test-IsInvariant {\r\n    param([string]$Content)\r\n    \r\n    $invariantPatterns = @(\r\n        \"^## (Active|Pending|Completed)\",\r\n        \"^### (Phase [0-9]|Key|Insi)\",\r\n        \"^\\- \\[ \\]\",\r\n        \"^(Goals|Notes):\",\r\n        \"^# (CURRENT|ACTIVE)\",\r\n        \"^[0-9]+\\. .*(phase|goal|architecture)\"\r\n    )\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($pattern in $invariantPatterns) {\r\n        if ($Content -match $pattern) { return $true }\r\n    }\r\n    return $false\r\n}\r\n\r\n# ============================================\r\n# PULSE LOG PROCESSING\r\n# ============================================\r\nfunction Get-PulseLogs {\r\n    param([string]$Pattern)\r\n    \r\n    $logs = Get-ChildItem -Path $Pattern | Sort-Object Name\r\n    if ($logs.Count -lt $MinPulseCount) {\r\n        Write-Warning \"Need at least $MinPulseCount pulses, found $($logs.Count)\"\r\n        return @()\r\n    }\r\n    return $logs\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Parse-PulseContent {\r\n    param([string]$Path)\r\n    \r\n    $lines = Get-Content $Path\r\n    $structured = @{\r\n        Invariants = @()\r\n        Variants = @()\r\n        Raw = ($lines -join \"`n\")\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($line in $lines) {\r\n        if (Test-IsInvariant -Content $line) {\r\n            $structured.Invariants += $line\r\n        } else {\r\n            $structured.Variants += $line\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return $structured\r\n}\r\n\r\n# ============================================\r\n# PREDICTION ENGINE\r\n# ============================================\r\nfunction Test-Prediction {\r\n    param(\r\n        [array]$CurrentPulse,\r\n        [array]$NextPulse\r\n    )\r\n    \r\n    $matchCount = 0\r\n    $predictableItems = $CurrentPulse | Where-Object { \r\n        $_ -match \"^(Phase|Goal|TODO|Next)\" \r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($item in $predictableItems) {\r\n        if ($NextPulse -match [regex]::Escape($item)) {\r\n            $matchCount++\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    if ($predictableItems.Count -eq 0) { return 0.0 }\r\n    return $matchCount / $predictableItems.Count\r\n}\r\n\r\n# ============================================\r\n# MAIN EXECUTION\r\n# ============================================\r\nWrite-Host \"=== TIC Classifier - Temporal Invariance Compression ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"\"\r\n\r\n$pulseLogs = Get-PulseLogs -Pattern $LogPattern\r\nif ($pulseLogs.Count -eq 0) { exit 1 }\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Processing $($pulseLogs.Count) pulse logs...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\r\nWrite-Host \"\"\r\n\r\n$results = @()\r\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt $pulseLogs.Count - 1; $i++) {\r\n    $current = Parse-PulseContent -Path $pulseLogs[$i].FullName\r\n    $next = Parse-PulseContent -Path $pulseLogs[$i+1].FullName\r\n    \r\n    $invRatio = if (($current.Invariants.Count + $current.Variants.Count) -gt 0) {\r\n        $current.Invariants.Count / ($current.Invariants.Count + $current.Variants\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 08:10:49\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774354259097}}
